'''[[克羅埃西亞|克羅埃西亞]]'''（HR）包含在[[歐盟|歐盟]]的[[地域統計單位命名法|地域統計單位命名法]]（NUTS）中。該命名法於2007年初克羅地亞加入歐盟後，由{{link-en|克羅埃西亞統計處|Croatian Bureau of Statistics}}編纂並且制定<ref>{{cite journal | url = http://narodne-novine.nn.hr/clanci/sluzbeni/2007_04_35_1120.html | language = hr | title = Nacionalna klasifikacija prostornih jedinica za statistiku (NKPJS) | author = Croatian Bureau of Statistics | journal = Narodne novine | issue = 35/07 | date = 2007-04-02 | accessdate = 2012-04-15 | archive-date = 2009-05-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090530041333/http://narodne-novine.nn.hr/clanci/sluzbeni/2007_04_35_1120.html | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。該命名法最近修訂時間為2012年<ref name="HR-NUTS-2012">{{cite journal | url = http://narodne-novine.nn.hr/clanci/sluzbeni/2012_08_96_2161.html | language = hr | title = Nacionalna klasifikacija prostornih jedinica za statistiku 2012. (NKPJS 2012.) | author = Croatian Bureau of Statistics | journal = Narodne novine | issue = 96/2012 | date = 2012-08-22 | accessdate = 2012-09-10 | archive-date = 2015-06-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150622124252/http://narodne-novine.nn.hr/clanci/sluzbeni/2012_08_96_2161.html | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>Lider: [http://liderpress.hr/fight-club/Podjela-Hrvatske-na-dvije-statisticke-regije/ Podjela Hrvatske na dvije statističke regije] {{Wayback|url=http://liderpress.hr/fight-club/Podjela-Hrvatske-na-dvije-statisticke-regije/ |date=20151208205143 }}, "Continental" and "Adriatic".</ref>。

該命名法分成三種等級<ref name="HR-NUTS-2012"/>：
* NUTS-1：克羅埃西亞
* NUTS-2：2個地區（非行政區）
* NUTS-3：21個[[克羅埃西亞行政區劃|縣]]

